12.short_description: Advanced payment & sales platform with analytics for small/medium retail businesses. More than a processor, it streamlines operations.

18.description:
Xell emerges as a game-changer in the retail industry, particularly for small and medium-sized businesses. This advanced platform transcends traditional payment processing, offering an integrated suite of tools designed to streamline business operations, enhance sales strategies, and provide in-depth analytics.

- Advanced Payment Processing: At its core, Xell provides reliable and secure payment processing solutions, accommodating various payment methods to cater to a diverse customer base.

- Sales Enhancement Tools: The platform includes specialized tools aimed at boosting sales. These tools help businesses in creating effective sales strategies, managing promotions, and optimizing pricing.

- In-Depth Analytics: One of the standout features of is its analytics capability. The platform offers comprehensive data analysis tools that provide valuable insights into sales trends, customer behavior, and business performance. This feature helps businesses make informed decisions and tailor their strategies for maximum impact.

- Customer Relationship Management (CRM): The integrated CRM system allows for efficient management of customer data, enabling personalized customer interactions and fostering loyalty.

- Point of Sale (POS) System: The intuitive POS system simplifies transactions, ensuring a smooth and efficient checkout process for both staff and customers.

- Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) Features: Xell incorporates essential ERP functionalities, aiding in inventory management, financial accounting, and overall resource planning, which are crucial for the seamless operation of retail businesses.

- User-Friendly Interface: The platform is designed with user experience in mind, featuring an intuitive interface that is easy to navigate, ensuring that users can fully utilize its features without extensive technical expertise.

- Customization and Scalability: Understanding the diverse needs of retail businesses, Xell offers customizable solutions that can be tailored to specific business requirements. Its scalable nature ensures that it grows with your business, adapting to changing needs and expanding capabilities.

In summary, Xell is not just a payment processor but a comprehensive solution for small and medium retail businesses. It combines advanced payment processing with powerful sales, analytics, and business management tools, all within a user-friendly interface, making it an indispensable asset for modern retail operations.

12.short_description: Indoor vertical farming solutions using smart hydroponics.

Our growing systems / vertical farms are 170x more efficient than traditional farming, use 95% less water and require minimal supervision. These are modular and scalable, with the food production capacity of the equivalent of 1 acre in only 27m2. This future of food production and sustainability: Farm to table, just a few steps away with our Growing as a Service model.

12.short_description: SharyCo makes sustainability part of the organization's DNA by rewarding employees for carrying out sustainable and solidarity actions.

18.description:
Organizations face growing demands from their stakeholders to take action toward sustainability, but the main barrier to achieving sustainability goals is the organization's own culture.  


Sharyco is the online platform companies need to hardwire sustainability into organizational culture. 


Collaborators build sustainable habits by completing Actions and Challenges for points and prizes. These habits create a sustainable lifestyle, reflected in users’ Sharyco feeds and point-based rankings, that inform performance reviews.
The platform also hosts a collaborative economy where community members can share products, services, and favors with each other using the points they earn. A dashboard provides HR and Sustainability Leaders with quantifiable metrics and evidence for sustainability reports.  


Sharyco provides a framework for planning and managing sustainability efforts, unifies rewards programs, and improves talent fidelity and retention, building employer branding.


All this results in a lasting culture shift, hardwiring sustainability into the organization’s DNA.
